examples.en: The way they argue is almost comical.
I must have looked comical in that big hat.
The note of pure panic in his voice was almost comical.
It was a comical sight to see her mince along.
When he gets angry, he talks in a sort of agitated jabberwocky that is really quite comical.
As the war went on, precision bombing became a comical oxymoron relished by bomber crews with a sense of black humor.
